      <title>公布业绩后，伯克希尔估值将逼近 1 万亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-26/berkshire-set-to-close-in-on-1-trillion-valuation-after-results</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伯克希尔哈撒韦公司 (Berkshire Hathaway Inc.) 股价周一盘前交易中上涨高达 5.5%，涨幅超过 10%。如果它在整个交易日持续存在——将使该集团的市值进一步接近 1 万亿美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-26/berkshire-set-to-close-in-on-1-trillion-valuation-after-results</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 26 Feb 2024 10:30:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>受欢迎的中国掉期交易降温，表明债券需求下降</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-26/popular-china-swap-trade-cools-signaling-lower-demand-for-bonds</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，一些金融机构已经减少了美元兑换人民币的规模，这表明外国对中国债券的需求可能会放缓。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-26/popular-china-swap-trade-cools-signaling-lower-demand-for-bonds</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 26 Feb 2024 10:22:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>阿达尼绿色氢能部门计划获得高达​​ 30 亿美元的贷款</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-26/adani-green-hydrogen-unit-aims-to-get-up-to-3-billion-in-loans</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，阿达尼新工业有限公司正在就筹集最多 30 亿美元的资本支出进行谈判，该公司是印度港口电力集团的子公司，旨在成为该国绿色氢能发展的主要参与者。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-26/adani-green-hydrogen-unit-aims-to-get-up-to-3-billion-in-loans</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 26 Feb 2024 10:09:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>世贸组织总干事认为贸易增长逆风的预测缺失</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-26/wto-chief-sees-trade-falling-short-of-forecasts-on-weaker-growth</link>
      <description><![CDATA[世界贸易组织 (WTO) 总干事恩戈齐·奥孔乔-伊韦阿拉于 2024 年 1 月 19 日星期五在瑞士达沃斯举行的世界经济论坛 (WEF) 闭幕日举行的小组会议上。一年一度的达沃斯论坛政治领导人、高层管理人员和名人的聚会将于 1 月 15 日至 19 日举行。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-26/wto-chief-sees-trade-falling-short-of-forecasts-on-weaker-growth</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 26 Feb 2024 09:50:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>丹麦放弃北溪爆炸探测器，未造成刑事案件</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-26/denmark-ends-nord-stream-investigation-without-criminal-case</link>
      <description><![CDATA[丹麦放弃了对 2022 年导致其领海外北溪天然气管道破裂的爆炸事件的调查，邻国瑞典本月早些时候也做出了类似的决定。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-26/denmark-ends-nord-stream-investigation-without-criminal-case</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 26 Feb 2024 09:22:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
